Dr. Yoban Shetty is the best person to get your braces from. I got my teeth aligned through braces from him. My treatment took a total of 3 years. During the entire time he has been really friendly and treated my teeth extremely well. I was very lazy with wearing my rubbers, but he made sure my teeth weren’t affected due to the same. Also to keep my teeth in place after the removal of my braces, he made sure they were splinted well and took care of them time and again. I am extremely happy with how they look right now, and I’m ever grateful for my smile. I really really recommend him!
